Third-party components
----------------------

The core engine depends only on the Python standard library. Development and
CI use ruff (linting) and pytest (tests); these are build-time tools, not
redistributed with the engine. Optional session-search (`okfmem index` /
`search`) uses Python's bundled SQLite (FTS5) — no third-party runtime deps.
